column1: # There are certain rules to be followed while trying to create input data that is in compliance with a nested tuple definition.
# a) Top level tuple attribute names should NOT be mentioned here.
# b) Empty nested tuples must be fully expanded with their correct attribute names assigned to dummy values i.e. {name1=dummyValue1
# c) Non-empty nested tuples must be fully expanded with their correct attribute names assigned to actual values i.e. {name1=value1
# d) Empty lists and maps can be indicated by [] and {} respectively.
